long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Nature Wallpapers New Tab turns new tab to custom themes with nature wallpapers.

Install this extension to enjoy varied HD nature wallpapers in your start and new tab page.

Features
- Shuffle of fix wallpaper on new tab
- Quicklinks to most used app
- Date and Time
- Google search
